WEBVTT

00:06.428 --> 00:08.530
You know, it says, "Out of Workshop" for a reason.

00:09.005 --> 00:11.539
I'm so sorry to bother you, boss, but something has come up,...

00:11.633 --> 00:12.697
...and it's kind of a big deal.

00:12.839 --> 00:13.593
What is it?

00:13.705 --> 00:15.457
Have you ever heard of the World Cup?

00:16.212 --> 00:18.977
Well, they moved it to the holidays.

00:19.723 --> 00:19.915
Wait.

00:20.501 --> 00:23.343
